text: Her cyð on þysum gewrite þa forewearde þe Ælfwine bysceop & se hyred on ealdan mynstre worton wið Osgoð þa hy letan him to þæt land æt Eadburgebyrig wið þan lande æt Wroccesheale þe he binnan Wiht hæfde.

Þæt wæs þæt Osgod bruce þæs landes æt Eadburgebyrig his deg & hæfter his dege ga þæt land eft into ealdan mynstre mid mæte & mid mannum & mid eallum þingan swa swa hit stande eall swa hy hit him ær to handa leton.

Þyses is to gewitnesse, Eadweard cingc & Ælfgsyfu seo hlefdige & Eadsige arcebiscop & Ælfric archebisceop & Brihtwold biscop & Lyfincg biscop & Duduc biscop & Æþestan biscop & Eadnod biscop & Ælfwerð biscop & Grimcytel biscop & Godwine eorl & Leofric eorl & Siwerd eorl & Swegen eorl & Ordgar & Odda & ælfgar & þærtoeacan manig god mann ægðær ge hadode ge lewede þe heora naman ne magon beon hær on ealle amearcode.
Þyssa gewrita syndon þreo, an is on ealdan mynstre, oþer is mid þæs bisceopes landbocan, þridde hæfð Osgod.
